---
title: Beef Burgers with Roasted Wedges and Zesty Cilantro Mayo
description: A caliente combo of beef and cilantro meet in this Mexican-inspired burger! Crispy potato wedges and a wholesome green salad make for satisfying sides.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-au-chorizo-94d1a80d.jpg
